Subject: [R-sig-DB] Storing data.frame attirbutes in SQL through DBI
In-Reply-To: <dba1e14b0709290730u552239d5y7074f9fd5758751e@mail.gmail.com>
References: <dba1e14b0709290730u552239d5y7074f9fd5758751e@mail.gmail.com>
